de.tudarmstadt.ukp.dkpro.core.ngrams.util

Class NGramStringListIterable

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tudarmstadt.ukp.dkpro.core.ngrams.util.NGramStringListIterable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<List<String>>

    public class NGramStringListIterable
extends Object
implements Iterable<List<String>>
    Creates a NGram iterable from a list of tokens. It does not detect any sentence boundaries. Thus, one should make sure to only add lists that reflect a sentence or a phrase.
